Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain

Class Enemy

java.lang.Object
nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain.Enemy
public abstract class Enemy
extends java.lang.Object
This abstract class represents an enemy that moves in a predetermined path. If the player moves into this enemy, it will DIE. If the enemy moves into this player, it will DIE.
